anced-data\"><td colspan=\"30\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"12\">Monster ID</th><td colspan=\"18\">823</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"30\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Melzar the Mad chathead.png\" src=\"/images/Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png?3f44f\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"103\" height=\"102\" data-file-width=\"103\" data-file-height=\"102\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Melzar the Mad</b> is one of the three wizards, along with <a href=\"/w/Thalzar\" title=\"Thalzar\">Thalzar</a> and <a href=\"/w/Lozar\" title=\"Lozar\">Lozar</a>, who escaped from <a href=\"/w/Crandor\" title=\"Crandor\">Crandor</a> when the <a href=\"/w/Dragon_(race)\" title=\"Dragon (race)\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/w/Elvarg\" title=\"Elvarg\">Elvarg</a> destroyed it, and is the only one of them to have survived. He has since lost his sanity, leading to his nickname, and has secluded himself and his <a href=\"/w/Map_parts\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Map parts\">piece of the map to Crandor</a> in <a href=\"/w/Melzar%27s_Maze\" title=\"Melzar&#39;s Maze\">his maze</a> north-west of <a href=\"/w/Rimmington\" title=\"Rimmington\">Rimmington</a>. He is fought during the <a href=\"/w/Dragon_Slayer_I\" title=\"Dragon Slayer I\">Dragon Slayer I</a> quest.\n</p><p>In combat, Melzar can kick, punch, cast <a href=\"/w/Fire_Strike\" title=\"Fire Strike\">Fire Strike</a> or a <a href=\"/w/Curse_spells\" title=\"Curse spells\">Curse spell</a>, or cast a <a href=\"/w/Spell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Spell\">spell</a> that produces a <a href=\"/w/Cabbage\" title=\"Cabbage\">cabbage</a> in a random spot in the room. (Note that the cabbages <b>CAN</b> be used for <a href=\"/w/Food\" title=\"Food\">food</a>.)\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Location\">Location</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Location\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Location\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable align-center-3 align-center-4 autosort=1,a\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Location\n</th>\n<th>Levels\n</th>\n<th>Members\n</th>\n<th>Spawns\n</th>\n<th>Map\n</th></tr>\n<tr><td><a href=\"/w/Melzar%27s_Maze\" title=\"Melzar&#39;s Maze\">Melzar's Maze</a> Basement</td><td class=\"\">43</td><td><a href=\"/w/Free-to-play\" title=\"Free-to-play\"><img alt=\"Free-to-play icon.png\" src=\"/images/Free-to-play_icon.png?628ce\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" data-file-width=\"16\" data-file-height=\"16\" /></a></td><td>1</td><td><a class=\"mw-kartographer-maplink\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/3/2/-1/2929/9649\" data-zoom=\"2\" data-lat=\"9649\" data-lon=\"2929\" data-mapid=\"3\" data-plane=\"0\" data-overlays=\"[&quot;pins&quot;]\">Maplink</a></td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Because Melzar the Mad is insane, while fighting, he says things that don't make sense.\n</p>\n<ul><li>Feel the wrath of my feet!</li>\n<li>Let me drink my tea in peace.</li>\n<li>By the power of custard!</li>\n<li>Leave me alone, I need to feed my pet rock.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"18 June 2007\"><a href=\"/w/18_June\" title=\"18 June\">18&#160;June</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2007\" title=\"2007\">2007</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:The_Dragonfire_Shield\" title=\"Update:The Dragonfire Shield\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>The NPC was renamed from \"Melzar the mad\" to \"Melzar the Mad\".\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Dragon Slayer I\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Dragon_Slayer_I\" title=\"Template:Dragon Slayer I\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Dragon_Slayer_I\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Dragon_Slayer_I?action=ed